          <h3>Angel's Wings Children</h3>
          <p><strong>Bio:</strong> Angel’s Wings Children is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization that aims to advocate for palliative care and palliative care centers around the globe. They partner with the Beijing Pediatric Palliative Care Center and serve as a day-time activity center for children with serious blood or cancer related conditions.</p>
          <p class="black-link"><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://angelswingschildren.org/" target="_blank">https://angelswingschildren.org/</a></p>
